{"tid":2082503,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩日本電影推介？","createTime":"2020-06-28T05:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T14:37:15.000Z","uid":159323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"708aa04db4938b70ecdc7e39efacc9e263daf83d","tid":2082503,"uid":159323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"個人比較鍾意既導演係矢口史靖同埋土井裕泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 以下就係我既心水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greenmamahk.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/e593aae5958ae593aae5958ae7a59ee58ebbe69d91_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmamahk.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F09%2Fe593aae5958ae593aae5958ae7a59ee58ebbe69d91_02.jpg&h=b21f2a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《戀上春樹》<br />\n好鍾意日本鄉村風土人情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.zhuzhudy.com/resize/w320,h0/movie/cover/133903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.zhuzhudy.com%2Fresize%2Fw320%2Ch0%2Fmovie%2Fcover%2F133903.jpg&h=062a019e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《藉着雨點說愛你》<br />\n好touching既親情同愛情，我覺得係超越《在世界中心呼喚愛》既純愛電影經典<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cu4FRAgVYAAYIZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCu4FRAgVYAAYIZW.jpg&h=4a43c709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《奇蹟補習社》<br />\n熱血到爆，好有當年考公開試既感覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/allison220/1438624968-2538260155_wn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fallison220%2F1438624968-2538260155_wn.jpg&h=4807e80f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《歌舞伎町24小時時鐘酒店》<br />\n多線發展，每個喺歌舞伎町打拼既人都有自己既故事，我覺得係嚴重underrated 既作品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/2539261409/TB2rwjReXXXXXbnXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!2539261409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi3%2F2539261409%2FTB2rwjReXXXXXbnXXXXXXXXXXXX_%21%212539261409.jpg&h=d0bb7ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《深夜食堂》<br />\n心靈雞湯，睇完好平靜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201308/90c3464d1e506fb903b278026faec80c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201308%2F90c3464d1e506fb903b278026faec80c.JPG&h=e26f2b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《言葉之庭》<br />\n大城市小故事，雨景好靚，個人認為係新海誠最高傑作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊擺低你既心水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e574cd0dab430715dd150755213298ef59eb1efa","tid":2082503,"uid":270073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"死亡預告幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e6a77c42adce0535986666d958c30793c32fb8","tid":2082503,"uid":70977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"覺得日文嘅文學同電影都好 <br />\n劇情唔洗太離奇古怪 唔係嘩眾取寵咁<br />\n平平淡淡咁都已經好好睇<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得古都 日日是好日都幾正嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefd49904c835380602f851eb8795aa895e3305f","tid":2082503,"uid":309526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"PPPD-355 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f47320b675726e6d3e10b1990a9255607fc1798","tid":2082503,"uid":64345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"海猿"},{"pid":"8a1d93c60782a32b04da8edbe68a77396b4af828","tid":2082503,"uid":109124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f47320b675726e6d3e10b1990a9255607fc1798","tid":2082503,"uid":64345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"海猿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"嗰種熱血真係冇一套可以比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a336477e08ae6cc0cd192159f5e84142c2d3b486","tid":2082503,"uid":15235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020